<para style="q1">

<verse number="3" style="v" />They conspire against your people</para>

<para style="q1">and plan together against your protected ones.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="4" style="v" />They have said, "Come, and let us destroy them as a nation.</para>

<para style="q1">Then the name of Israel will no longer be remembered."</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="5" style="v" />They have schemed together with one strategy;</para>

<para style="q1">against you they have made an alliance.</para>
